item.description: Friday Dec 3rd our holiday meetup! It is going to be so much fun...giveaways and a yankee swap!! Last year we had a ball!! Please bring a wrapped gift ($10 give or take). Please make it raw or kitcheny or eco friendly... or all 3 and funny is always good! :) As I am writing this I am smiling because I know how much fun it is going to be. Raw Vegan potluck. Bring an organic raw dish enough for 6-8 people. If you are new and not sure what to bring a salad...fruit or veggie is always good. Can't wait to party with all of you!

group.name: Manchester Raw Vegan Food Meetup Group

item.name: Dec Meetup!! Dec 3rd!!
